Title: S5 Ep. 229 IWS Video Team
Description:
This week's episode is very special as we say thank you to our video editing intern team from Cat 5 Studios Josue Gonzalez, Geo Vargas, Lester Echols, and Deena Burks. 

In this episode you will hear what they learned from their internships, what their PowerSkills are, and what they think the video industry will look like in 2030. We hope you look them up on LinkedIn and be sure to listen to our podcast or watch our show on the Employers 4 Change YouTube channel.
